[{"Code":"en","Title":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Slug":"draft-th-cards-direct-acquiring","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mmvfwcgz-odli4o-001\"><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\" display=\"false\"></a></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmvfwch0-s6cofp-002\"><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\" display=\"false\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch1-vd4l83-003\"><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch2-84234p-004\"><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch2-ris8e0-005\"><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch2-pugyrc-006\">Sales/ CS</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch3-d6j2nv-007\">Submitting the request</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch3-2fvjik-008\">MO</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch3-vfn333-009\"><a><u>Kavissara (Praew) ApiratrueangwutKittapat (Pingpong) Srisuphan</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch3-n11aib-010\">Activate channels</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmvfwch3-xsj6iw-011\"><a id=\"_l0o6jdyv2txv\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmvfwch3-3z32yq-012\"><a id=\"_hbvftyg2k24s\" display=\"false\"></a>Eligibility</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch4-2p1ric-014\"><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch4-x7nxw6-015\"><strong>Eligible</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch4-y9kkro-016\">Sole Proprietorship</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch4-v98ryx-017\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-tcqt8s-018\">Corporation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-dl6ycq-019\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-dncpm2-020\">Non-Local Entities</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-637w3q-021\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-skqeq5-022\">Partnership</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-3ygjqf-023\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-f7vvok-024\">Non-Profit</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-udy3jp-025\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmvfwch5-8jt4al-026\"><a id=\"_pusnju68rku5\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmvfwch6-zs43zm-027\"><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch6-tevwjj-029\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch6-iizysz-030\"><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch6-km4aeg-031\">Integration Method</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch6-i158rh-032\">Only available for merchants integrating via Payments API or Cards (Charge API).</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch6-032g9p-033\">MID Setup</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-fxv9g9-034\">Each merchant must have at least 2 MIDs <strong>(1 for Visa, 1 for Mastercard)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-s15phu-035\">Card Schemes</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-m2c55s-036\">Supports Visa and Mastercard only but cannot process local Thailand debit cards.</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-4ngqiz-037\">Limitation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-fmpk6r-038\"><strong>Payment Links</strong> cannot be used with Silverflow unless the merchant is also onboarded to Cybersource or MPGS.</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-fesnzj-039\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-73a8ea-040\"><strong>Entity Origin</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-msdlnd-041\"><strong>SLA</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch7-4dz9mv-042\">All entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-0wyo2p-043\">2 to 6 weeks</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-id2qdm-044\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-7pdtpf-045\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-bd6jp8-046\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-kbxa6h-047\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-cteqhd-048\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-gtaqef-049\">Channel Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch8-12zf69-050\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch9-3n3tqf-051\">Silverflow (direct acquiring)</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmvfwch9-195zs0-052\"><li data-block-id=\"mmvfwch9-an2hv6-053\"><p>Only to be used when a merchant integrates through payments API or cards (charge API). Payment links can not be used, unless the merchant is also onboarded to Cybersource or MPGS.</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch9-1ja6dk-054\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch9-o2jmal-055\">Risk Approval</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch9-7a6wpl-056\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwch9-wg53au-057\">MO to request Mrisk’s approval. Consult the Mrisk department to confirm if the merchant is eligible for direct acquiring rails.<br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\">Note: Only escalate to Mrisk only High risk merchant and Merchant with TPV &gt;20k USD as their SOP</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwcha-gygoy7-060\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwcha-cug7zb-061\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwcha-3ei718-062\">Once approval from Mrisk is received, proceed in activating channel via retool</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmvfwcha-nfr7x7-063\"><a id=\"_iw137qmfzes3\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmvfwcha-rkm6l7-064\"><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\" display=\"false\"></a>Activation Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwcha-gfhs4v-065\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchb-2npatg-066\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchb-jefqxn-067\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchb-j7x781-068\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchb-r5ex9h-069\">Channel Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchb-92r0ba-070\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchb-v9hf9z-071\">Use <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/b4787d82-1cc0-11ef-8834-d340ecb2f27d/Channel%20Approval/Payment%20Setting%20UI\"><u>retool</u></a> to activate the channel.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchb-epg5jy-072\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchc-9zri4p-073\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchc-mmtnej-074\">Input the Business ID (#1) with the merchant BID (can be seen in admin dashboard) and set Transacting Entity (#2) to Xendit Thailand then click Next (#3).<br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmvfwchc-09re9s-077\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-cards-direct-acquiring-image-76n2whzk.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchc-5blbaw-078\"><img data-block-id=\"mmvfwchc-3h3mgx-079\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-cards-direct-acquiring-image-pbcqrk8s.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchd-swul6k-080\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchd-ri5ezy-081\">Set payment method (#1) to CARDS and Partner (#2) to Direct Acquiring (Silverflow - Visa and Mastercard) then click next (#3).</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchd-soar68-082\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-1akzp3-083\">In this part, MO needs to input business detail, address, and some other information.</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-nkyp8k-084\"><li data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-79holl-085\"><p>Input Mcc (#1) with the right MCC for the specific merchant. MO should already know the right MCC during KYC process</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-kgcam4-086\"><li data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-0y3q7e-087\"><p>MCC checking tool: https://xendit.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ICA/pages/4317610002/Find+the+correct+MCC</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-n1qnhp-088\"><p>Then click Next (#2)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-tlu20h-089\"><img data-block-id=\"mmvfwche-5aavdg-090\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-cards-direct-acquiring-image-hiq4325z.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-pqji8a-091\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-kdujhp-092\">MO can just skip this page and click Activate! (#1).</p><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-43s83d-093\"><img data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-1ybfae-094\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-cards-direct-acquiring-image-kofp2fkh.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-9oqsa0-095\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-7bq4hy-096\">cards activation DONE.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-nsymcd-097\"><img data-block-id=\"mmvfwchf-47lf99-098\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-cards-direct-acquiring-image-c3iqwebo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmvfwchg-hn49ri-099\"><a id=\"_eo8f2o4hqql8\" display=\"false\"></a>Rejection Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchg-bhtjwg-100\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchg-ikgdmx-101\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchg-p39l8a-102\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchg-w14kih-103\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchg-ujjkwy-104\">1.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchg-8m64s0-105\">If a merchant fails onboarding criteria, the MO agent notifies the requester via the original submission channel:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmvfwchh-40sheh-106\"><li data-block-id=\"mmvfwchh-9aku52-107\"><p>CS: Inform the team to relay the result to the merchant.\t</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmvfwchh-hpcpv8-108\"><p>Direct MO: Respond to the existing email thread.\t</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmvfwchh-6t0cjw-109\"><p>Sales/Slack: Reply within the #mo-request or #thailand-pg-activation-request thread.</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmvfwchh-unrgpx-110\">MO</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p></p>","SeoTitle":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Slug":"th-cards-direct-acquiring","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Slug":"th-cards-direct-acquiring","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Slug":"th-cards-direct-acquiring","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"TH Cards (Direct Acquiring)","Description":null}]